$ Oracle: SQL plan management
@ SQL plan management

*SQL plan managment* monitors → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement/execution/plan[execution plans] over time in order to check if they deteriorate. With SQL plan management, stability
of an → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement/execution/plan[SQL plan] can be guaranteed, especially when upgrading the database or optimizer version.

*SQL plan management* is preferred over *stored outlines*.

Enhancements for SPM in 12c include
  • Automatic plan evolution
  • Enhanced auto capture
  • Capture from AWR repostitory

sa:
  *SQL plan management* is an «option», see → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/option[`v$option`]
